messages.content: Noel Armando Delgadillo added Deacon Noah Thelen and Jono Taccolini to the group.

Hi guys, Hope you enjoyed Memorial Day.  A reminder that we'll be practicing today at Calvin at 6pm. If you can make it great! I know Tuesday isn't our normal day but trying to get in as many reps before the tournament! Fields by the track, next to the parking lot.  See ya there, bring your water!
Noel Armando Delgadillo added Jay Gabbard to the group.
Next week we wont have practice on the Monday because of Memorial Day, but Tuesday we'l head out to the Calvin fields but the track at around 6pm.

Hi Bro,  Hope all is well with on this fine morning! We have some pick up soccer tonight on the field north of Houseman Field. Parking on Lyon St. From 6-7:30pm, hot dogs and more back at my place afterward.
